InclusionRules.name: Admission/discharge time
InclusionRules.description: Admission and a discharge time could be retrieved

InclusionRules.name: Opioid prescription +/- 30
InclusionRules.description: Patients who have at least one opioid prescription overlaps with the time range +/- 30 days around surgery

InclusionRules.name: Encounter before/after surgery
InclusionRules.description: Patients who have at least 2 encounters in time range [2 years before surgery ; 30 days before] and at least 2 encounters in time range [30 days after; 2 years after surgery]

InclusionRules.name: No second surgery
InclusionRules.description: Patients who did not undergo another surgery in the prolonged opioid window (2-7 months after surgery)

InclusionRules.name: No death one year after surgery
InclusionRules.description: Patients who have at least 1 encounter more than 2 years after surgery
